         Windows App SDK and WinUI
         ====================================================================
         
         ⚠️ CRITICAL: DO NOT DOWNGRADE Microsoft.WindowsAppSDK BELOW 1.8.3
         
         Versions 1.6.x and 1.7.x contain a fatal bug (RemovePayloadDuplicates task)
         that causes build failures with telemetry assembly errors.
         
         Reference:
    https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/apps/windows-app-sdk/stable-channel#version-183-18251106002
         ==================================================================== -->
    <PackageVersion Include="Microsoft.WindowsAppSDK" Version="1.8.251106002" />
